    "name": "CRI-O Metrics API",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "description": {
      "content": "The CRI-O metrics endpoint exposes Prometheus-compatible metrics for operations, image pulls, container lifecycle, and runtime errors. Metrics are enabled with the --enable-metrics daemon flag and served on the port configured by --metrics-port (default 9090) at the /metrics path. The endpoint can also be served over a Unix socket via --metrics-socket and secured using --metrics-cert and --metrics-key for TLS.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: CRI-O Project",
      "type": "text/plain"
    }
